snippet.title: Conqueror's Blade – Season VII Cinematic Trailer Featuring ‘Galgaldr’ by Heilung
snippet.description: Ragnarok is coming to Conqueror’s Blade, and an epic new saga is about to begin. Hear the dire prophecy of the Seeress in the official cinematic trailer for Season VII: Wolves of Ragnarok, set to launch as a free update on March 18! This trailer features the song ‘Galgaldr’ by Heilung, taken from their 2019 album Futha. Find out more: https://conqblade.com/news/751
